profile:
Old World Woodworking & Millwork's tradition starts with a clear understanding of the character and vision of your space so that the project can be planned well. It continues with quality workmanship and is followed up with a personal guarantee of quality.
We build and design kitchens, wall units, antiques reproductions, built-ins, custom trim, custom doors and wood storm windows. Restoration and repairs. We design and build a variety of mill work including standard and custom trim, interior/exterior doors, storm windows, hand rails, mantles, wall units, kitchens as well as any kind of decorative wood work.
Check out our photos at www.oldworldwoodworking.com
